{"tid":429222,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)銀翼殺手","createTime":"2017-10-08T16:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T18:39:50.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"25c932c209eadd1b0aff6fa1dab37b5a997bb492","tid":429222,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=GGkYHCSLLDUlLL8Sja8vw4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=219c766e\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V台入佢主頁睇先比較順<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=GGkYHCSLLDUlLL8Sja8vw4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b7a33bf7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> dailymotion執柒左 好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=GGkYHCSLLDUlLL8Sja8vw4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=da98206a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/53/Blade_Runner_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F53%2FBlade_Runner_poster.jpg&h=b3260afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019年11月的洛杉磯，退職警察瑞克&middot;戴克（Rick Deckard，哈里遜&middot;福特 飾演）被官員蓋夫（Gaff，愛德華&middot;詹姆士&middot;奧莫斯 飾演）截住，蓋夫帶他去見老長官布萊恩（Bryant，麥克&middot;艾密特&middot;沃許 飾演）。身為一名「銀翼殺手」，戴克的工作是追捕被稱為人造人的生化機器人，並令他們「退役」（「殺死」的委婉說法）。布萊恩告訴戴克近來幾位「連鎖六型」（Nexus-6）人造人非法來到地球，他們僅有四年壽命，可能來地球尋求延長生命的方法。<br />\n戴克觀看了一名名叫霍登（Holden，摩根&middot;保羅 飾演）的銀翼殺手對某工廠員工進行測驗的畫面，這是一種人性測驗（&quot;Voight-Kampff&quot; test），透過人造人對問題的同理心反應，來從人類中區分出他們。該試驗的對象李昂（Leon，布瑞恩&middot;詹姆士 飾演）在霍登問及他母親的事之後，開槍將他打成重傷。布萊恩想戴克令李昂和其他三位人造人：羅伊&middot;貝提（Roy Batty，魯格&middot;豪爾 飾演）、左拉（Zhora，瓊安娜&middot;卡西迪 飾演）和普莉絲（Pris，黛瑞&middot;漢娜 飾演）退役。戴克起初拒絕接受新任務，但在布萊恩的間接威脅之下，不情願地接受了<br />\n <br />\n1 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=GGkYHCSLLDUlLL8Sja8vw4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c44d3b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=GGkYHCSLLDUlLL8Sja8vw4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=727441df\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08be2a0ea978339dfb56e310fe1bfa338dee2a85","tid":429222,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de08904bdd8e587eb805f9c535184bc9ce9cbd71","tid":429222,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face